cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI 

This paper deals with anomaly detection in network traffic data, which is a common topic in computer security (cs.CR) and network infrastructure (cs.NI) research. The paper also proposes the use of machine learning techniques (cs.AI) and compares the performance of the framework on different hardware setups (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper focuses on real-time detection of anomalies (cs.SI).
